%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20news%20came%20to%20Joseph%20Lobo%2C%20he%20did%20not%20immediately%20believe%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20the%20mango%20variety%20was%20rare%20and%20expensive%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20costly%20it%20could%20be.%20My%20family%20and%20friends%20consumed%20the%20first%20yield%2C%20unaware%20of%20its%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20farmer%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobo%20grows%20the%20Miyazaki%20Mango%20which%20is%20a%20Japanese%20variety%20known%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347996%2Frare-mangoes-available-in-india-alphonso-sindhri-mango-expensive-mangoes-summer-season%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20farmers%20in%20India%20who%20have%20successfully%20harvested%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20variety%2C%20Lobo%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349834%2Ffive-tips-to-grow-fruit-trees-at-home-mango-guava-on-terrace-gardening-indian-flowers-sushma-reddy-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrows%20other%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20including%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20flowers%20on%20his%20terrace%20farm.%20And%20the%20best%20part%3F%20He%20only%20uses%20organic%20fertilisers%20and%20techniques%20such%20as%20hydroponics%20to%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20this%20humble%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20magnificent%20farm%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98All%20I%20have%20is%20a%20terrace%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Udupi%2C%20Lobo%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20I%20had%20kno