ns%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Feathers%E2%80%99%20which%20upcycles%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20peers%20abandoned%20him%2C%20the%20faculty%20was%20impressed%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20come%20up%20with%20various%20ideas%20to%20tackle%20the%20chicken%20butchery%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20took%20him%20nearly%2013%20years%20to%20find%20success%20in%20this%20field.%20%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20many%20organisations%20like%20Tribes%20India%2C%20simultaneously%20focussing%20on%20my%20research%20work.%20It%20all%20started%20with%20a%20college%20project%20but%20the%20more%20I%20got%20into%20it%2C%20I%20found%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20data%20on%20this%20waste%20and%20people%20only%20talk%20about%20plastic%20waste.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20draw%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%20butchery%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Radhesh%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Feathers%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20upcycles%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre%20and%20handmade%20paper.%20Using%20this%20waste%20as%20raw%20material%2C%20the%20startup%20manufactures%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20stoles%2C%20diaries%2C%20fish%20feed%20and%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20plastic%2C%20waste%20that%20needs%20urgent%20attention%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20doctors%20in%20Fatehpur%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Radhesh%20was%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20medical%20field.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20design%20and%20craft%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20graduation%20in%20textile%20design%20from%20the%20Northern%20India%20Institute%20of%20Fashion%20Technology%20(NIIFT)%2C%20Mohali%2C%20and%20later%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Craft%2C%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20students%20who%20come%20to%20study%20in%20these%20colleges%20are%20from%20affluent%20and%20superior%20backgrounds.%20They%20would%20come%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346052%2Findian-startups-turning-waste-into-eco-friendly-products-trash-to-treasure-watch-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearn%20about%20design%20and%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20thoughts%20didn%E2%80%99t%20align%20with%20that%20and%20I%20was%20nothing%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20manufactures%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20stoles%2C%20diaries%2C%20fish%20feed%20and%20manure%20from%20chicken%20waste.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-2-1718797540-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20manufactures%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20stoles%2C%20diaries%2C%20fish%20feed%20and%20manure%20from%20chicken%20waste.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20worked%20all%20day%20handling%20butchery%20waste%20for%20my%20research%2C%20I%20used%20to%20stink%20as%20well.%20People%20would%20not%20stand%20near%20me%20and%20I%20felt%20excluded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Radhesh%20engrossed%20himself%20in%20his%20research%20work%2C%20and%20it%20was%20then%20that%20he%20understood%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20the%20third%20largest%20wet%20waste%20problem%20worldwide.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20causes%20of%20river%20pollution.%20There%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20data%20on%20this%20waste%20but%20we%20estimate%20that%20about%2032.17%20percent%20of%20total%20waste%20in%20rivers%20like%20Ganga%20and%20Yamuna%20is%20butchery%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Environment%20Education%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceeindia.org%2Ffile%2FPOULTRY-waste-mangement-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEE%3C%2Fa%3E)%20mentions%20that%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20broiler%20meat-producing%20country%20after%20the%20USA%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20China%2C%20with%20over%204.6%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20annual%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20CEE%20is%20a%20national%20institute%20dedicated%20to%20enhancing%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20environment.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpoultry%20waste%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20as%20a%20formal%20management%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20estimated%20that%20the%20generation%20of%20poultry%20waste%20is%20approximately%2020%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20just%20within%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bpoultry%20waste%5D%20is%20either%20sold%20to%20middlemen%20(for%20proces